   - **apps/app/src/app/(app)/(user)/(pending-not-allowed)/_components/client-auth-bridge.tsx** (full rewrite + biome auto-format)
     - Why: central handshake component — discriminated union on mode, POST branch, didStart latch (merged from Phase 3), Sentry on error paths, "success" status.
